Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Shining Armor\Nand Princess Cadance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,don't think it's too\Nsoon for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to come back to the Crystal\NEmpire for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just know Flurry Heart's\Ngrown so much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll\Neven recognize her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only baby\Nthey have, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be pretty easy\Nto figure out who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I know you want to visit\Nyour niece as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm excited to\Nsee Sunburst again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want\Nto fall behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,on my friendship\Nlessons back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, your work in\NPonyville isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think we\Nall know you can learn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,about friendship\Nanywhere, right Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike? Who's Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh you're\NSpike, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you\Ndressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! You're blowing my cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you even\Nknow it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're YOU-- in\Na coat, hat, and glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we're the\Nonly ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, why do you\Nneed a disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time we came\Nto the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a lot going\Non with the new baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Crystalling,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still got\Nmobbed in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say "mobbed."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is just\Na family visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want the presence of\N"Spike the Brave and Glorious"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn it into\Nsome kind of circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it. The Crystal\NPonies adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He did save the\NEmpire. Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I don't\Nthink your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,will turn our visit\Ninto a circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if I find the right\Ndisguise, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\NBy YayPonies\NWe have crystal muffins!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.no/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh disguise or not, Spike, I\Ndon't think you need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,about being mobbed.\NNopony's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad\Nfeeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't need\Nthe disguise after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Spike, the\NBrave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's come to save\Nus yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Spike! Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Save you from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was everypony hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure looks like Princess\NTwilight and her pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can we be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't. Either one of them\Ncould be the-- you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What if this isn't\Nthe real Spike!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,EVERYPONY RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Something strange\Nis definitely going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you don't recognize\Nthe Princess of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we recognize her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't\Nmean it's really her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, guys.\NThey're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And any friend of Spike\Nthe Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is a friend of the Crystal\NEmpire, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. It does look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we'll need to see\Nsome proof of identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We'll take care of{\i0}\N{\i1} things from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Cadance, thank\Ngoodness! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can explain, Twilly\Nif it really is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sunshine, Sunshine--"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"--Lady bugs awake! Clap your\Nhooves and do a little shake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, everypony.\NIt's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's her.\NWhat's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A Changeling's been\Nspotted nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A Changeling!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After Queen Chrysalis took\Nmy place at our wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and invaded Canterlot\Nwith her army of minions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not taking any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Changelings feed off of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and ever since Flurry\NHeart's Crystalling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the Empire is filled with more\Nlove than anywhere in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible they've\Ncome for the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've posted the\Nextra guards and why we're--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--checking\Neverypony's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Flurry Heart's really been\Nlooking forward to seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's gotten so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I will do whatever\Nwe can to help protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, having you\Nhere is already a big relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Royal Guards were\Nwondering if Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the Brave and Glorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,would like to join in the\Nsearch for the Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't know if that's\Nsuch a good idea, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight. This is\NSpike the Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking to. Have you ever\Nknown me to run from danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ummmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be safe with our guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will your guards\Nbe safe with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, the Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've faced the evil\NChangelings before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Um. Well, they are\NChangelings, so they can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that? These monsters\Ncan look like any of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so be on guard, guards.\NEven more than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And they could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we should cover as\Nmuch ground as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You, search that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you search that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll just search\Nhere, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many places to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless that rock\Nis a Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, "rock", how do I know\Nyou're really a rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm not talking, huh?\NWell, you can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Maybe it's time Spike\Nthe Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,went back to, ah,\Nprotect those guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. Just my reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha hah! Hmm, just my\Nimagination, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,AUGGGGGHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-ch-ch-changeling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAHHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAHHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The ice is pretty slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want you to\Nget hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You... saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. I know you\Ndon't want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Changelings\Nare supposed to be evil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil? Oh, not me. All I've\Never wanted is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment I first split\Nmy egg in the nursery hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was part of the\Nattack on Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,during the Royal Wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd never seen true\Nfriendship like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't just steal\Nit and feed on its love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I knew I couldn't\Nlive with my kind anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I set off looking for\Nlove to share. But--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's so much love in\Nthe Crystal Empire right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what drew me here,\Nbut it's driving me crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be from\Nthe Royal Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty much a giant\Noutpouring of light and love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for a new baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.\NI'm just so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a friend, maybe the\Nlove we shared could sustain me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think the Crystal\NPonies want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I told you there was\Nsomepony they respect and admire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so much, he could convince\Nthem to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If only that were true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is! I mean, I\Nam. It's ME! Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike? The Brave and Glorious?\NI'm sure you've heard of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I was raised by\Nan evil queen. I'm Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you\Nwant to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Hasn't anypony ever\Njust been nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry! Kindness\Nlike that kind of brings it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still want\Nto be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! And I am one\Nhundred percent sure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get the whole Crystal\NEmpire to be your friend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But, maybe I should just uh,\Ntalk to them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? Did\Nyou see the Changeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you defeat\Nthe evil creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating a Changeling\Nwould be brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you know what\Nwould be glorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating two Changelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating all the Changelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not having to fight\Nthe Changeling at all
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because I made\Nfriends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha hah! Oh. Wow. For a second\NI thought you were serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! Could you imagine?\NFriends with a Changeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am serious. He\Nwants to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only are you Spike\Nthe Brave and Glorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're also Spike\Nthe Hilarious! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking. The\NChangeling is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,HA HA HA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But I don't\Nthink it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Changeling Queen,\NChrysalis, kidnapped Cadance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and cast a spell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing\Nas a nice Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Shining Armor.\NSorry. That was a... bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So? So! What did they say? How\Nmany new friends do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it didn't go\Nexactly the way I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I understand. Well,\Nthanks for trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess it's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you expect ponies\Nwho look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To trust something\Nthat looks like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, if you're done\Nsearching for the Changeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I\Ncould use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working on a protection\Nspell for Flurry Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and nopony takes\Nnotes like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh actually, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to introduce\Nyou to my friend, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...Crystal! ...Hoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal Hoof, my good\Nfriend, Crystal Hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, it's nice to meet you\Ntoo. How do you know Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike and I go way back--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--to the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when we met. We've\Nbeen pen pals ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pen pals! Spike, you could have\Nbeen using my pen pal quill set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I-I pretty much\Nonly write to him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,when you and Starlight\Nare studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to brag to all my\Nfriends about my letters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,from Spike the\NBrave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Starlight\Nand I can manage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to spend\Ntime with your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Crystal Hoof promised\Nto take me around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal Hoof is nearly as\Nentertaining as Spike himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This place is everything\NI've ever dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't keep\Npretending
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a Crystal\NPony forever, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, you're winning them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, nopony will care\Nthat you're a Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight told me you\Nwere off with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And any friend of Spike\Nthe Brave and Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh she's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much LOVE\Naround her. I-- I--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I'm so sorry!\NI can't-can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, get away\Nfrom the Changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! No! You\Ndon't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This Changeling replaced your\Nfriend to get close to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What other explanation\Ncould there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After it! Don't let\Nthe Changeling escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope your friend is OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you should\Ngo find Crystal Hoof
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,while we hunt down\Nthe Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he\Ndoesn't want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread out! The Changeling\Nis probably still nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm\Npretty sure he ran
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as far away from\Nhere as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet I know where!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to apologize. I\Nshould have stood up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Thorax.\NI know you're in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I would help\Nyou? I'm an evil Changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish I had\Nbeen one to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. I know it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the Crystal\NEmpire loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask you to\Ngive that up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What I should have done\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move, move, move, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you checked there?\NLook around that corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's bad that\Nthere's a Changeling around,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but is all this\Nreally necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's one Changeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there may well be a\Nwhole army on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,True, but Starlight\Nhas a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting a\Nlittle out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, but I don't\Nknow what else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! What are you doing?\NGet away from that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's not a thing. His name\Nis Thorax. And he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Would you say I'm a{\i0}\N{\i1} hero, glorious and brave ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ If I told you something{\i0}\N{\i1} you wouldn't believe? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That sometimes I'm scared{\i0}\N{\i1} and I can make mistakes ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And I'm not so{\i0}\N{\i1} heroic, it seems ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But if day can turn to night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the darkness{\i0}\N{\i1} turn to light ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Then why can't we imagine{\i0}\N{\i1} a Changeling can change? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ No two ponies are{\i0}\N{\i1} exactly the same ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ No two snowflakes ever{\i0}\N{\i1} match their design ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And I thought I was strong,{\i0}\N{\i1} but I was nothing but wrong, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ When I forgot to be{\i0}\N{\i1} friendly and kind. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But if day can turn to night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the darkness{\i0}\N{\i1} turn to light ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Then why can't we imagine{\i0}\N{\i1} a Changeling can change? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Would you say I'm a{\i0}\N{\i1} hero, glorious and brave ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ If I told you something{\i0}\N{\i1} you wouldn't believe? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This Changeling it{\i0}\N{\i1} seems, knows the real me. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And would stay by my{\i0}\N{\i1} side till the end. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ So if day can turn to night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the darkness{\i0}\N{\i1} turn to light ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Then why can't we imagine? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just why can't we imagine,{\i0}\N{\i1} then why can't we imagine ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ the Changeling can change? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm so\Nproud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! You're a celebrity\Nhere in the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just risked\Nall of it for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine anything\Nmore brave than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Princess of Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to set an example\Nfor all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, it was Spike who\Ntaught me that a new friend
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,can come from anywhere.\NI guess everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,still has things to learn\Nabout friendship, even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Spike says Thorax is his\Nfriend, then he's my friend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the Crystal Empire,\NI would like to extend my hoof
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in friendship and I am\Nsure all of my subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are eager to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Crystal\NEmpire, Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we didn't take the\Ntime to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can change that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be so amazing! I want\Nto know all about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe one day I can\Ntake that knowledge back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Changeling Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If my kind learned how to\Ncreate love for one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe they wouldn't have\Nto take it from others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To Spike the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you were\Nright after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship lessons\Ncan happen anywhere.
